<section id="annotation">
  <title>DMLex Annotation Module</title>
  <para>This module makes it possible to mark up substrings inside the string values of certain
    objects and to attach properties to them.</para>
  <para>It is up to the implementer to decide how to implement annotations, whether as
      <emphasis>inline markup</emphasis> (as XML) or as <emphasis>stand-off annotations</emphasis>
    (for example through start and end indexes).</para>
